Package org.apache.jackrabbit.ocm.nodemanagement.exception

Exception Summary
BaseNodeManagementException Base exception for all JCR Node Type Management exceptions.
NamespaceCreationException Exception that is thrown when a JCR namespace could not be created.
NodeTypeCreationException Exception that is thrown when a JCR node type could not be created.
NodeTypeRemovalException Exception that is thrown when a JCR node type could not be removed.
OperationNotSupportedException Exception that is thrown if a JCR operation is not supported by a JCR repository implementation.
